## Overview

Add a comprehensive Personal Analytics Dashboard widget that visualizes productivity metrics, trends, and insights across all modules (Tasks, Time Tracking, Notes, Events). Provides actionable insights to help users understand their work patterns and optimize productivity.

## Problem Statement

Users currently lack visibility into their productivity patterns:
- **No metrics** - Can't see completion rates, time spent, or trends
- **No insights** - Don't know peak productivity hours or patterns
- **No goals** - Can't track progress toward objectives
- **Fragmented data** - Metrics scattered across different modules

**Use Cases:**
- **Freelancers:** Track billable hours, project time, completion rates
- **Students:** Monitor study time, assignment completion, productivity trends
- **Professionals:** Analyze meeting time, deep work blocks, task velocity
- **Personal:** Daily/weekly reviews, habit tracking, goal progress

